Initial configuration:
Heimdall shall have a installation and configuration web page for technicians who configure the devices and sensors. Technician shall have the provision to enter the following details
a. Customer name
b. Site name
c. Building details
    i. Building name
    ii. Floor count
    iii. Floor details
        1. Floor position
        2. Sensor count
        3. Sensor details
            - Sensor name
            - Sensor Type

Modify configuration:
Technician can add, delete or modify the details in the webpage. 